Package org.biogeomancer.validation

Class Summary
AbstractDataMap An abstract class starting to implement the Map interface based on the data structure of either BioGeomancer interpretations or original records.
BGConcepts Utility class statically defining all concepts needed by the DataTester framework.
DivaLookup Class used by ElevationErrorTest, GeographicErrorTest and ProbabilityProxyTest to read data from geospatial raster and vector files.
EcologicalOutlierResult Wrapper class giving programmer-friendly access to ecological outlier results.
ElevationError Wrapper class giving programmer-friendly access to a specific elevation error.
ElevationErrorResult Wrapper class giving programmer-friendly access to elevation error results.
EnvironmentalOutlier Individual result for an environmental outlier related to some record.
EnvironmentalOutlierResult Wrapper class giving programmer-friendly access to environmentl outlier results.
GeographicError Wrapper class giving programmer-friendly access to a specific geographic error.
GeographicErrorResult Wrapper class giving programmer-friendly access to geographic error results.
InterpretationDataMap Extends AbstractDataMap and represents a concrete Map interface implementation representing BioGeomancer interpretation records, where each interpretation is tied to an original record.
InterpretationRecordSet An adapter class to use the interpretations of a BioGeomancer record set as a GenericRecordSet in the data tester framework context.
ItineraryOutlier Wrapper class giving programmer-friendly access to itinerary outlier results related to a specific record.
ItineraryResult Wrapper class giving programmer-friendly access to itinerary outlier results.
NumericOutlierResult Wrapper class giving programmer-friendly access to numeric outlier results.
OriginalRecordDataMap Extends AbstractDataMap and represents a concrete Map interface implementation representing original BioGeomancer records.
OriginalRecordSet An adapter class to use the original records of a BioGeomancer record set as a GenericRecordSet in the data tester framework context.
SpatialAttributeLookup  
ValidationManager Manager class responsible for data validation.
